hwSessionsJson.summary: Session 20: Feature verification run completed (all 10 systems pass). Cleaned 30 stale worktrees + 39 branches. Ran deliberation on SaaS opportunities -- concluded with TaxCreditCalculators.com (solar lease vs buy calculator, content + lead gen model). Scaffolded new project at C:\Users\Patri\CascadeProjects\tax-credit-calculators with CLAUDE.md, prototype, and deliberation docs. Moved hello-world MCP server from global to project-scoped config to prevent cross-project bleedover. Switching to tax-credit-calculators project next.
